com.inrix.sdk.model

Class Itinerary

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inrix.sdk.model.Itinerary

  • public final class Itinerary
extends Object
    An Itinerary is a collection of scheduled Trips. A scheduled Trip is an instance of a Trip at a specified date/time. For a one time Trip this may be the one instance of the Trip, but for recurring Trip there may be many instances of the Trip which occur between the Itinerary.getStartDate() and Itinerary.getEndDate().
